extends AbsMusicServiceActivity
implements com.sothree.slidinguppanel.SlidingUpPanelLayout.PanelSlideListener, AbsPlayerFragment.Callbacks
    作者:
    Karim Abou Zeid (kabouzeid)

    Do not use AppCompatActivity.setContentView(int). Instead wrap your layout with wrapSlidingMusicPanel(int) first and then return it in createContentView()
